c: 17
v: 51
t: "Kapa eng le eng feela e hlotsoeng e thata kahar’a likelello tsa lona!” Ke moo ba tla re: “Joale ke mang ea tla re busetsa bophelong hape?” E re: “Eena Ea le hlotseng sethathong.” Ba tla u sisinyetsa lihlooho, ba re: “Seo se tla fihla neng?” E re: “Kamohlomong seo se tla etsahala haufi-ufi"